   </div>  <h1 class="article-heading" role="heading" itemprop="headline">Could these be the worst year-end bonuses ever?</h1> <div class="information clearfix no-image">       <div class="author ">   <div class="author-information story-meta no-image" itemprop="author">    By  Maria Atanasov </div>     </div>       <ul class="tags"><!--   --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/ethics" class="ethics">Ethics</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/good-business" class="good-business">Good Business</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/20141104-holiday" class="holiday">Holiday</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/leadership" class="leadership">Leadership</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/managing" class="managing">Managing</a> </li><!--     --><li> <a href="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/capital/tags/spending" class="spending">Spending</a> </li><!--      --></ul>   </div>   <div class="social">       <!--[if lte IE 8]><span class="s-b-ie s-b-ie8"><![endif]--> <!--[if gt IE 8]><span class="s-b-ie s-b-iem"><![endif]--> <div class="s-b-container s-b-en-gb" data-version="0.4.1" data-variant="default" data-language="en-gb" data-ptrt="http://www.bbc.com/modules/share/close"> <div class="s-b s-b-default"> <form action="/web/20150105212223/http://www.bbc.com/modules/share/page" method="get"> <input type="hidden" name="app_id" value="58567469885" id="sb-1-sb-1app_id"><input type="hidden" name="shareUrl" value="http://www.bbc.com/capital/story/20141205-the-worst-bonuses-ever" id="sb-1-sb-1shareUrl"><input type="hidden" name="image" value="http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/wwfeatures/976_549/images/live/p0/2d/l2/p02dl2cs.jpg" id="sb-1-sb-1image"><input type="hidden" name="redirect_uri" value="http://www.bbc.com/modules/share/close" id="sb-1-sb-1redirect_ur